text: Karin Keller-Sutter (born 22 December 1963) is a Swiss politician and the President of Switzerland in 2025. She has been a Member of the Swiss Federal Council since 2019. She is a member of FDP.The Liberals. She was the Vice President of Switzerland in 2024.
